git-hawser-init(1) -- Ensure Git Media is configured properly.
=============================================================

## SYNOPSIS

`git hawser init`

## DESCRIPTION

Init performs the following actions to ensure Git Media is setup properly:

* Sets up the clean and smudge filters under the name "media".
* Installs a pre-push hook to run git-hawser-push(1)

## SEE ALSO

Part of the git-hawser(1) suite.
